# NLP Text Classifier (Bug / Feature / Other)

This project is a simple NLP (Natural Language Processing) classifier that categorizes user issue sentences into three categories:

- **Bug**
- **Feature Request**
- **Other**

It uses the TF-IDF vectorization technique to convert text into numerical form and a Naive Bayes classifier for prediction.  
This project is beginner-friendly and demonstrates the basic NLP workflow.

